    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Idle是等待状态，Processing是处理中，Complete是完成准备输出。转换条件是start和finish。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Processing",
        "Complete",
        "start",
        "finish"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出框架：MQTT Broker指向Idle，然后Idle通过start事件转到Processing，Processing通过finish事件到Complete，最后Complete连到ActuatorController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "Idle",
        "Processing",
        "Complete",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
