      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认：Broker单向触发Idle，整个链路是单向的。那我用stateDiagram-v2来实现，保持标准语法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
